short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extracts detailed data from any Invoice with +99.99 accuracy. Supports PDFs and Photos.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
DocDigitizer Invoice Extractor provides a free service to extract data from invoices with accuracy above 99,99%. You can send invoices in PDF format or a Photo,

Install the extension to add the DocDigitizer button to the email compose toolbar. Click DocDigitizer logo and then choose Extract. The extension will add "extract+invoice@docdigitizer.com" to the "To:" field.
Just attach an invoice to the email and click send. 

You'll receive an email back with the invoice data summary and two files: txt and json, will the full detailed invoice information.

Have fun.

Available for US and Europe.
